cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper presents a method for training vision-based control policies on real robots.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper uses reinforcement learning to train the control policies.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is relevant as the method involves learning vision-based control policies.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the method involves using auxiliary tasks to improve learning efficiency.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper deals with control policies for a physical system (robot arm).
